Sankei Building Co Ltd is issuing a 60mln dlr equity warrant eurobond due May 7, 1992 paying anindicated coupon of 2-1/8 pct and priced at par, lead managerNomura International Ltd said.    The issue is guaranteed by Sumitomo Bank Ltd and isavailable in denominations of 5,000 dlrs. The sellingconcession is 1-1/2 pct while management and underwritingcombined pays 3/4 pct. The payment date is May 7 and listingwill be in Luxembourg.    Final terms will be fixed on April 15. The warrants areexercisable from May 21, 1987 until April 23, 1992. REUTER&#3;